it is needed to install to the build server

  sudo apt-get install libgtk-3-dev libgtkmm-3.0-dev libssl-dev libpcsclite-dev Xvfb

depending on your architecture get the right chrome version
64 bit -
  wget https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb
32 bit -
  wget https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_i386.deb

install downloaded chrome:
  sudo dpkg -i google-chrome*.deb

to build:
  make clean && make

to install after the build phase
  sudo make install

to test
  make clean && make test

